{"tid":1378660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我宣布] 我頂唔順了 求求大家幫下我","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:21:24.000Z","uid":40217,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb1ac1e0d2617b8f0510c2d2c1f76ad38a8eb18","tid":1378660,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"話我標題黨又好乜都好，但真係好想講出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運動過左咁耐了，我地一直都好團結<br />\n<br />\n雖然冇乜進展，但係見到香港人團結起來、爭取自由，就會覺得我地會有希望會贏。但經過727、728，見到有好多post前線同和理非互屌。<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">求下大家和解好嗎？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確，各人都有立場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>前線</strong></span>有佢地嘅諗法，加上落場形勢瞬息萬變，又冇人統籌，好多時靠臨場反應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>和理非</strong></span>係現場又好、冷氣軍師又好，大家都係擔心前線，大家都係想件事好。佢地接收嘅訊息又比較多同快，見到危險嘅時候想叫現場走都好正常。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我宣布，互屌埋今晚就算了</span></strong>，求下大家。我哋仲有好多野要做，仲有好多困難要我地解決。<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e83bcbf3c1ed1efea2e304f5e70d79bf0924e7","tid":1378660,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fe526757cfc0da4d2ee32562fac572bd3a06e93","tid":1378660,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"斷網, 去多幾次澳門首家線上賭場"},{"pid":"e0442653ef6dbce4658190e734af7b52eb259176","tid":1378660,"uid":239472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45f49a1a7b71ce5d3cb6f95c1bbbc054c45aea7","tid":1378660,"uid":2